```cpp
#define DEBUG_PT              // Paper tape operations
#define DEBUG_FLOPPY_PIO      // Floppy PIO operations
#define DEBUG_FLOPPY_DMA      // Floppy DMA operations
#define DEBUG_DATATRANSFER_PIO // PIO data transfer details
#define DEBUG_DETAIL          // Detailed operation logs
#define DEBUG_INTERRUPT       // Interrupt handling
```

Set in `NDBus.h`:
```cpp
#define DEBUG_BIF 1  // Bus interface debugging
```

